 in 2016 - a groundbreaking proof for which Viazovska was awarded the Fields Medal in 2022. The book is suitable for self-study by graduate students or advanced undergraduates with an interest in complex analysis and its applications, or for use as a textbook for graduate mathematics classes, with enough material for 2-3 semester-long classes. Researchers in complex analysis, analytic number theory, modular forms, and the theory of sphere packing, will also find much to enjoy in the text, including new material not found in standard textbooks.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aAsymptotische Analyse. 4aDas Euler-Gamma und Riemannsche Zetafunktionen. 4aElliptische Funktionen. 4aKugelpackung. 4aModulare Formen.  aComplex analysis, analytic functions, complex integration, complex variables,.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Mathematics 2023 Englishz978311131920908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Mathematics 2023z9783111318608oZDB-23-DMA0 cEPUBz97831107968890 cprintz978311079678040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110796810zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110796810zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110796810/original  a978-3-11-131920-9 EBOOK PACKAGE Mathematics 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2 EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2023  aZDB-23-DMAb2023  aZDB-23-GOA